description: AlarmPort: This table records alarm events on specific ports of radio access network equipment, detailing the alarm's characteristics, location, and status.  dateTime: Timestamp of alarm; Area_Name: Geographic location of the equipment; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site; Id2: Redundant cell ID; Id3:  Secondary ID (likely internal); Id4:  Another secondary ID; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; AlarmPort.userLabel: User-defined label; AlarmPort.administrativeState: Administrative lock status; AlarmPort.perceivedSeverity: Severity level of the alarm; AlarmPort.alarmSlogan: Description of the alarm; AlarmPort.alarmPortId: ID of the port in alarm; AlarmPort.filterDelay: Delay before alarm triggers; AlarmPort.availabilityStatus: Availability state; AlarmPort.operationalState: Operational state of the port; AlarmPort.filterTime: Filter time; AlarmPort.filterAlgorithm: Filter algorithm; AlarmPort.normallyOpen: Normally open/closed state; AlarmPort.alarmInExternalMe: Alarm status in external management entity.
